Hi.

This directory includes the sources of some fixed Blitz 1.90 libraries.
I don't know if Acid will correct them in a later version.


fixes in gtlib:
- Memory Loss (40 bytes) for each GTGadget allocated.
- Added a GTArea command to replace GTShape (it was incorrect).

fixes in palettelib:
- USE PALETTE now works correctly under OS2.xx

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note:
If you want to see the fixes, search for the "MIK" string in the source.
